-- MTN May Acquire a Stake in India's Loop Telecom, Business Standard Reports
-- Rakteem Katakey
-- 2010-06-28T01:46:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/mtn-may-buy-as-much-as-45-stake-in-india-s-loop-telecom-standard-reports.html

          
          
             South Africa’s MTN Group may
purchase a stake in India’s Loop Telecom, which has been looking
for an investor and is willing to sell as much as 45 percent in
the company, the Business Standard reported without saying where
it got the information.  
